{
  "info": {
    "name": "CIMS — Coaching Institute Management (Backend)",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the CIMS NestJS backend.\n\n**Deployed base URL:** `https://cimsapi.gogreenbingo.in` (default `baseUrl`). Use `{{localBaseUrl}}` (http://localhost:3000) to point at a local run instead.\n\n**Surfaces**\n- Tenant API  → `/api/v1`  (institute users: admin/teacher/student/parent, JWT via TenantAuthGuard)\n- Platform API → `/platform/v1` (SaaS super-admins: owner/support, JWT via PlatformAuthGuard)\n- Root        → `/health`, `/webhooks/razorpay` (public)\n\n**Auth**\nLogin requests auto-capture `accessToken`/`refreshToken` into collection variables via test scripts. Tenant folder requests send `{{tenantAccessToken}}`; Platform folder requests send `{{platformAccessToken}}`.\n\n**Seeded platform owner (change in production):**\n- email: `owner@cims.test`\n- password: `OwnerPass123!`\n\n**Getting started**\n1. `baseUrl` is already set to the deployed server.\n2. Run `Platform Auth › Login` (owner creds above are pre-filled) → token auto-captured.\n3. `Tenants › Provision tenant` creates an institute + its admin (sets `tenantId`).\n4. Set `subdomain` to the one you provisioned, then run `Tenant Auth › Login`.\n5. Fill id variables (studentId, batchId, etc.) as you create resources — most create requests auto-capture their `_id`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "https://cimsapi.gogreenbingo.in" },
    { "key": "localBaseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "subdomain", "value": "acme" },
    { "key": "tenantAccessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tenantRefreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platformAccessToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "platformRefreshToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tenantEmail", "value": "admin@acme.test" },
    { "key": "tenantPassword", "value": "changeit123" },
    { "key": "platformEmail", "value": "owner@cims.test" },
    { "key": "platformPassword", "value": "OwnerPass123!" },
    { "key": "studentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "batchId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "feePlanId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "invoiceId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "assignmentId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "submissionId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "testId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "materialId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "leadId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tenantId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "planId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "inviteToken", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tenant Auth (/api/v1/auth)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (b.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantAccessToken', b.accessToken);",
                  "if (b.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantRefreshToken', b.refreshToken);",
                  "pm.test('has tokens', () => pm.expect(b.accessToken).to.be.a('string'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"subdomain\": \"{{subdomain}}\",\n  \"email\": \"{{tenantEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{tenantPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (b.accessToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantAccessToken', b.accessToken);",
                  "if (b.refreshToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('tenantRefreshToken', b.refreshToken);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"{{tenantRefreshToken}}\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "refresh"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Accept invite",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"subdomain\": \"{{subdomain}}\",\n  \"token\": \"{{inviteToken}}\",\n  \"password\": \"newpassword123\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/accept-invite", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "accept-invite"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Invite user (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const b = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (b.inviteToken) pm.collectionVariables.set('inviteToken', b.inviteToken);",
                  "if (b.userId) pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', b.userId);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@acme.test\",\n  \"name\": \"New Teacher\",\n  \"role\": \"teacher\",\n  \"phone\": \"+911234567890\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/invite", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "invite"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register FCM token",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{tenantAccessToken}}" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"fcm-device-token-here\"\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/fcm-token", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "fcm-token"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Students (/api/v1/students)",
      "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{tenantAccessToken}}" }] },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List students",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "students"] } }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get student",
          "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students/{{studentId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "students", "{{studentId}}"] } }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create student (admin/teacher)",
          "event": [{ "listen": "test", "script": { "type": "text/javascript", "exec": ["const b = pm.response.json(); if (b._id) pm.collectionVariables.set('studentId', b._id);"] } }],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{userId}}\",\n  \"rollNo\": \"R-001\",\n  \"admissionDate\": \"2026-01-15\",\n  \"batchIds\": [\"{{batchId}}\"]\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "students"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update student (admin/teacher)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"rollNo\": \"R-002\",\n  \"batchIds\": [\"{{batchId}}\"]\n}" },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students/{{studentId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "students", "{{studentId}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete student (admin)",
          "request": { "method": "DELETE", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/students/{{studentId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "students", "{{studentId}}"] } }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Batches (/api/v1/batches)",
      "auth": { "type": "bearer", "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{tenantAccessToken}}" }] },
